#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:45
msgid "**Install prerequisite packages**"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:51
msgid "**Enable the deb.torproject.org repository**"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:53
msgid "Configure `apt` to pull packages from `deb.torproject.org`."
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:55
msgid ""
"```\n"
"bash -c 'dist=$(lsb_release -s -c); /bin/echo -e \\\n"
"\"deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/tor-archive-keyring.gpg] \\\n"
"https://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org $dist main\\n\\\n"
"deb-src [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/tor-archive-keyring.gpg] \\\n"
"https://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org $dist main\" \\\n"
"> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/tor.list'\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:64
msgid "**Import deb.torproject.org's GPG signing key**"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:66
msgid ""
"```\n"
"wget -qO- https://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org/"
"A3C4F0F979CAA22CDBA8F512EE8CBC9E886DDD89.asc \\\n"
"    | gpg --dearmor \\\n"
"    | tee /usr/share/keyrings/tor-archive-keyring.gpg >/dev/null\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/tor_hidden_service.md:72
msgid ""
"The signing key ensures the package retrieved from the server was created by "
"`deb.torproject.org`."
msgstr ""

